{"tid":774831,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"求戲名","createTime":"2018-08-10T15:44:11.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-10T15:49:57.000Z","uid":199536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"c01c07c9cc90c926105a9111a0efc1ff48e26529","tid":774831,"uid":199536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-10T15:44:11.000Z","msg":"講講我對套戲嘅印象先<br />\n以前好似係2010年嗰牌，喺明珠台睇過，佢重播我都睇過幾次，記得嗰時我係睇唔明套戲，覺得好奇怪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n內容好似有<br />\n背景係有成個宇宙噉大，有唔同星球<br />\n有一部金字塔噉嘅超級電腦，識講嘢，有人問佢條問題，佢用咗好多年諗個答案，最後佢答咗啲數字出嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n又有一幕話有個人喺度做緊一個新宇宙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n記憶得噉多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有冇巴絲知道我講邊套戲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e2f1541a3abee53768ecd69a0e92ae5f941e70b7","tid":774831,"uid":188688,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-10T15:46:15.000Z","msg":"The hitchhiker's guide to the galaxy"},{"pid":"0d1daae40365982087111ae760ba4fdfcacfc1d1","tid":774831,"uid":198583,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-10T15:48:54.000Z","msg":"九品芝媽菇"},{"pid":"0bd428256c1229f57b2d236217873d1ead1358fd","tid":774831,"uid":199536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e2f1541a3abee53768ecd69a0e92ae5f941e70b7","tid":774831,"uid":188688,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-10T15:46:15.000Z","msg":"The hitchhiker's guide to the galaxy"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-10T15:49:57.000Z","msg":"巴打幫我秒咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nth